Author: Fredde

REQUIREMENTS:
mms-1.1.0 rev-1560+
python 2.5 with sqlite3 support

BASEDIR variable:
Open the appletrailers.py script and change the BASEDIR 
variable. The dir it points to have to exist. This dir
will store the database and the downloaded trailer images.

The db will be created if it doesn't exist. If you want "fresh" 
trailers just delete the db-file (BASEDIR/appletrailers.db).

DOWNLOADDIR variable:
Open the appletrailers.py script and change the DOWNLOADDIR
variable. The dir it points to have to exist. This dir 
will store downloaded trailers.
